headline: This Internet Retailer And Three Other Stocks Outperforming The S&P 500
summary: Wayfair stock and three others were in or near buy zones in Monday trades. The internet retailer's relative strength line is at a new high.

headline: Howmet Aerospace to buy hardware business for $1.8B, among other M&A to end 2025
summary: South Korea-based Samsung Biologics plans to acquire its first U.S. manufacturing site, and Deere is expanding its technology services with the purchase of equipment management provider Tenna.
